<h1>SL-303 Async Queue & Job Governance</h1>
<p class="small">Prepared for: Morshed | Project: OraBooks Lean MVP | Date: 2026-06-27</p>

<h2>Executive Summary</h2>
<p>SL-303 is implemented and operational for Lean MVP scope. Verification was completed using project code evidence and fresh automated tests.</p>
<div class="box"><strong>Status:</strong> COMPLETE FOR MVP SCOPE</div>

<h2>Implemented Scope</h2>
<ul>
<li>Central async queue runtime with handler registry and scheduled worker.</li>
<li>Job lifecycle governance: pending, processing, completed, failed, dead_letter, cancelled, discarded.</li>
<li>Retry with exponential backoff and max-retry dead-letter transition.</li>
<li>Manual governance operations: replay, discard, cancel.</li>
<li>Heartbeat recovery for stalled processing jobs.</li>
<li>Queue monitoring: lag/dead-letter alerts and operational metrics.</li>
<li>Org-scoped security checks and cross-tenant replay protection.</li>
<li>Webhook dispatch signing support with HMAC headers.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Primary Evidence Files</h2>
<ul>
<li>includes/class-orabooks-async-queue.php</li>
<li>tests/OraBooks_AsyncQueue_Test.php</li>
<li>docs/openapi/openapi.json</li>
<li>orabooks-ui/src/components/platform/JobQueuePanel.tsx</li>
</ul>

<h2>Automated Test Result (Fresh)</h2>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> D:\xampp\php\php.exe tests\vendor\phpunit\phpunit\phpunit --configuration tests\phpunit.xml tests\OraBooks_AsyncQueue_Test.php</p>
<ul>
<li>Tests: 14</li>
<li>Assertions: 43</li>
<li>Result: PASS</li>
</ul>

<h2>How to Test Manually</h2>
<ol>
<li>Enqueue with idempotency_key and verify dedupe behavior.</li>
<li>Run success-path jobs and verify pending to processing to completed transitions.</li>
<li>Force failure and verify retry_count increment + next_retry_at backoff scheduling.</li>
<li>Exceed max retries and verify dead_letter transition + error capture.</li>
<li>Use replay/discard/cancel actions and verify allowed-state enforcement.</li>
<li>Test cross-tenant replay attempt and verify forbidden denial.</li>
<li>Verify queue metrics and Recent Failures in Job Queue panel.</li>
<li>Verify webhook HMAC headers for webhook_dispatch jobs.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Sign-Off Checklist</h2>
<ul>
<li>SL-303 unit tests pass.</li>
<li>Retry and dead-letter governance verified.</li>
<li>Manual operations (replay/discard/cancel) verified.</li>
<li>Org scope protection verified.</li>
<li>Monitoring and metrics verified.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Conclusion</h2>
<p>SL-303 Async Queue & Job Governance is complete and testable for OraBooks Lean MVP scope.</p>
<p><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Approve SL-303 for MVP sign-off.</p>
